00:34:55,812 --> 00:34:58,454
or there's lines that talk about your face,

836
00:34:58,655 --> 00:35:00,036
you would have to rewrite it also

837
00:35:00,176 --> 00:35:02,317
because you were an undead, even in the narrator notes,

