00:35:10,984 --> 00:35:13,346
And it turned out there was a lot of

843
00:35:15,655 --> 00:35:21,340
words describing the senses and the bodily structure of persons inside of the game.

844
00:35:21,380 --> 00:35:23,802
So there was a lot of rewrite happening as a result of that also.

845
00:35:28,265 --> 00:35:32,788
We'd been searching for the voice and the tone of the story for more than a year,

846
00:35:33,388 --> 00:35:35,709
and we finally figured it out.

847
00:35:36,330 --> 00:35:40,712
And we were all convinced, at least in the narrative and the writer team,

848
00:35:40,752 --> 00:35:43,393
that we needed to apply this throughout the entire game,

849
00:35:43,413 --> 00:35:45,054
because it was going to make the game that much better.

850
00:35:45,655 --> 00:35:51,197
So we fought with the producers' heart to get all of this stuff in.

851
00:35:51,958 --> 00:35:54,804
What you're looking at is what defined my summer in 2017.

852
00:35:54,984 --> 00:36:01,196
This is the file that was eventually generated somewhere in mid-July.

853
00:36:02,609 --> 00:36:05,830
It was a file with 80,000 lines of text in it,

854
00:36:05,950 --> 00:36:06,771
and more than a million words.

855
00:36:07,611 --> 00:36:09,171
And the little ones that you see

856
00:36:09,452 --> 00:36:11,312
meant that something was ready to record.

857
00:36:11,692 --> 00:36:13,373
And when the little one was put there,

858
00:36:13,393 --> 00:36:14,994
it meant that the situation had been reviewed,

859
00:36:15,014 --> 00:36:16,574
the dialogue line had been reviewed, it was okay,

860
00:36:16,614 --> 00:36:18,235
we were never gonna change it again in our lives.

861
00:36:19,095 --> 00:36:19,535
Which we didn't.

862
00:36:20,936 --> 00:36:23,337
But that meant that between July and August,

863
00:36:23,477 --> 00:36:25,617
as we were recording, by now in multiple studios,

