00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:36,204
And so it's fair to say that half of Original Sin 2 was written in those couple of months

867
00:36:36,925 --> 00:36:40,409
as a result of all of the delays that we've been accumulating.

868
00:36:40,609 --> 00:36:43,633
Luckily for us, we had a lot of writers and then we could handle it.

869
00:36:44,414 --> 00:36:45,855
But still, it was an insane job.

870
00:36:46,805 --> 00:36:48,686
It was Jan, our writing director,

871
00:36:49,867 --> 00:36:53,670
that to give you an idea of the level of iteration

872
00:36:53,690 --> 00:36:54,711
that we applied on this game,

873
00:36:56,493 --> 00:36:57,594
one week before release,

874
00:36:58,134 --> 00:37:00,116
I said, do you think I can still get this actress?

875
00:37:00,776 --> 00:37:05,060
And we changed the middle of the origin story of Sebil,

