00:37:50,576 --> 00:37:52,438
and your test plan is changing the entire time

895
00:37:52,458 --> 00:37:54,940
because somebody's changing the story the entire time,

896
00:37:55,020 --> 00:37:57,883
and even as you are supposed to test your finals,

897
00:37:57,923 --> 00:37:59,884
they're still flagging, this is ready,

898
00:38:00,005 --> 00:38:01,326
oh, this is not ready, let's change this,

899
00:38:01,406 --> 00:38:01,986
oh, this is ready.

