00:38:04,188 --> 00:38:06,010
So our QA team was actually,

902
00:38:07,812 --> 00:38:08,432
they were amazing.

903
00:38:09,333 --> 00:38:12,697
They had roadmaps that went through the game,

904
00:38:12,777 --> 00:38:14,199
that tested all of the permutations,

905
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:17,163
and they did a pretty good job,

906
00:38:17,283 --> 00:38:19,045
but it was arguably,

907
00:38:19,786 --> 00:38:21,868
well, needless to say.

908
00:38:22,722 --> 00:38:24,543
Not everything had been tested when we shipped

909
00:38:24,583 --> 00:38:25,443
because it was impossible,

910
00:38:25,463 --> 00:38:27,984
because since we kept on changing things continuously.

