00:38:47,511 --> 00:38:48,551
And the game was so large

922
00:38:49,051 --> 00:38:50,832
that if you started on Monday morning,

923
00:38:51,853 --> 00:38:55,116
of one week, then the Friday of the week after,

924
00:38:55,256 --> 00:38:56,617
you did one run through of the game.

925
00:38:56,858 --> 00:38:59,621
So you can imagine how much QA it took

926
00:38:59,801 --> 00:39:01,402
just to be able to do a permutation.

927
00:39:01,462 --> 00:39:04,145
And so as a result, we didn't have that much view

928
00:39:04,205 --> 00:39:05,847
of how the entire story played out

929
00:39:05,887 --> 00:39:08,289
because it just took too much time to go through it.

