00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:13,944
Luckily for us, it didn't matter that much that certain things didn't work because you

931
00:39:13,964 --> 00:39:16,245
couldn't necessarily notice when you played the game.

932
00:39:16,786 --> 00:39:21,830
Divinity had so much reactivity that if something didn't react, you didn't know if it was supposed

933
00:39:21,870 --> 00:39:22,730
to react or not react.

