00:40:38,687 --> 00:40:39,728
They wrote books about it.

963
00:40:40,128 --> 00:40:41,209
And we were very stubborn.

964
00:40:41,269 --> 00:40:42,570
We didn't want to change it because we said,

965
00:40:42,590 --> 00:40:44,012
well, they don't understand it's so accessible,

966
00:40:44,032 --> 00:40:44,992
everybody understands it, blah.

967
00:40:45,853 --> 00:40:48,495
And yeah, lots and lots and lots of discussions.

968
00:40:48,515 --> 00:40:50,957
There were an incredible amount of iterations

969
00:40:51,017 --> 00:40:53,880
inside of the company trying to save the armor system,

970
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:55,901
but essentially it remained a broken thing

971
00:40:55,921 --> 00:40:56,862
and it's something we shipped with,

972
00:40:57,443 --> 00:40:58,924
and maybe we shouldn't have shipped with it

973
00:40:58,944 --> 00:41:00,225
in the way that we did.

974
00:41:00,985 --> 00:41:06,771
The problem with it was that if you combine a damage shield together with control immunity,

975
00:41:06,831 --> 00:41:09,214
you limit your design space tremendously.

976
00:41:09,754 --> 00:41:12,777
And that's something that you don't really feel in the beginning of the game, which is

977
00:41:12,797 --> 00:41:17,942
what we had in Early Access, but you definitely feel it as you move towards Act 2 and Act 3.

978
00:41:19,340 --> 00:41:21,581
Another thing over which we traded a lot were the surfaces.

