00:41:35,764 --> 00:41:37,944
a steam cloud, and people liked it a lot

985
00:41:38,464 --> 00:41:40,745
because you could involve the environment in combat.

986
00:41:40,805 --> 00:41:43,465
So we figured that we should expand on this.

987
00:41:44,342 --> 00:41:46,483
And so this is one of many, many, many flowcharts

988
00:41:46,964 --> 00:41:50,486
of systems that we tried to get to surfaces better.

989
00:41:50,506 --> 00:41:54,129
And the thing was that, and we had those things executed.

