00:57:46,653 --> 00:57:49,174
And so later, when the fight starts,

1364
00:57:49,794 --> 00:57:51,175
that guy could not move at all.

1365
00:57:51,295 --> 00:57:54,657
So kind of, I don't know why you have this backdoor.

1366
00:57:54,677 --> 00:57:56,038
Is that deliberately designed?

1367
00:57:56,458 --> 00:57:58,279
Because I don't believe it's simply a bug.

1368
00:57:58,720 --> 00:58:00,801
So could you explain why you have that?

1369
00:58:02,322 --> 00:58:07,223
