1370
00:58:08,343 --> 00:58:15,146
you would not, your movement would not be locked, but you can, especially using the

1371
00:58:15,186 --> 00:58:19,907
sauna forest, that character, you can actually all summon a...

1372
00:58:20,247 --> 00:58:21,068
We did it on purpose.

1373
00:58:22,208 --> 00:58:23,148
So why do you have that?

1374
00:58:23,208 --> 00:58:25,489
We did it because we know that players like to glitch a game,

1375
00:58:25,649 --> 00:58:29,371
so we think it's a way of promoting player agency.

1376
00:58:29,511 --> 00:58:31,232
If they figure it out, they're very proud of it.

1377
00:58:31,792 --> 00:58:33,913
It's similar like, oh, I'm gonna talk to him

1378
00:58:33,953 --> 00:58:35,253
and then I'm gonna steal everything.

1379
00:58:35,493 --> 00:58:37,414
We leave that in because we know players like it,

1380
00:58:38,374 --> 00:58:39,995
even if it's obviously an exploit.

1381
00:58:40,815 --> 00:58:41,315
Okay, so.

1382
00:58:41,456 --> 00:58:42,336
So it's literally by design.

1383
00:58:43,187 --> 00:58:44,907
