00:59:17,460 --> 00:59:21,564
Hello, I'm just curious how you balance the crafting

1404
00:59:22,244 --> 00:59:24,466
connected to the combat, because there is clearly

1405
00:59:24,486 --> 00:59:27,148
a connection between the two for the arrows, the bombs,

1406
00:59:27,248 --> 00:59:28,029
and this kind of shit.

1407
00:59:29,731 --> 00:59:39,176
So our crafting was one of the things that we weren't very happy about and so we think that we could have done a much better job on the crafting so this is something it's a topic on its own.

