01:01:44,307 --> 01:01:46,629
So on the one hand, you don't want to be top-down heavy,

1446
01:01:47,149 --> 01:01:49,331
and you want to maximize what you get from the bottom up.

1447
01:01:49,391 --> 01:01:50,272
On the other hand, you still have

