01:01:51,252 --> 01:01:52,273
So I think this.

1450
01:01:53,073 --> 01:01:54,314
I don't have a ready solution for it.

1451
01:01:54,374 --> 01:01:55,114
I think it's a balance

1452
01:01:55,154 --> 01:01:57,095
that you're gonna have to walk continuously

1453
01:01:57,335 --> 01:01:58,956
and you're gonna have to adapt as you go

